==Places==
===United Kingdom===
*Stowe, Buckinghamshire, a civil parish and former village
**Stowe House
**Stowe School
*Stowe, Cornwall, in Kilkhampton parish
*Stowe, Herefordshire, in the List of places in Herefordshire
